{"tid":956842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"至尊重慶G煲個廁所真係好反智","createTime":"2018-12-26T15:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T05:13:00.000Z","uid":220068,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"760bf8099eac4f653c3f5dc91fbacd70778946a4","tid":956842,"uid":220068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:04:25.000Z","msg":"今日約咗班fd去mk創興食個至尊雞煲 慶祝boxing day<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為收工趕住去既關係就冇時間換返自己衫<br />\n當我入到佢個廁格換完衫開門嗰陣 先發現道門跟本冇任何手把<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eszs983.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEszs983.jpg&h=346affcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌安個鎖喺隔離塊板把撚咩<br />\n因為道門同隔離塊板唔啱size 所以要用力拍實道門先閂到<br />\n開門冇任何手把就更加麻煩on9<br />\n屌佢吖食食吓雞煲都比人囚禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我就用手指「new」少少門隙出黎 再攝手指入去嘗試撬開道門<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgOtUDw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgOtUDw.jpg&h=5be59148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但道弱智門又太實<br />\n咁我望到門上面唯一有既就係得條掛勾<br />\n我真係估唔到要用條掛勾黎開門 用上或下面門邊又驚污漕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VB5LW10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVB5LW10.jpg&h=e031c0f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但問題係拉個掛勾只係拉開到道門上面嗰part 整體仲係好實<br />\n都唔知幾多人屙完啲辣屎之後用手抆過枝野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至尊G煲係咪想我地食完辣G再去廁所集體玩辣屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁樣嘥咗我唔少食嘢既時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 變咗2個鐘都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話次次食親呢間野都有人生日 次次播埋同一首鬼死咁老土既生日歌<br />\n仲要全場都聽到 望晒去唱生日歌嗰枱 跟住引黎在場其他人既恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢間野真係不得了 各方面都撚化黎食嘢既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔知係咪特登<br />\n今日又係咁 呀壽星公你班fd真係大整蠱<br />\n我地嗰枱當時見到都覺老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf359792a7eb1de54ddeb6f45a679d98a87cf20b","tid":956842,"uid":67455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:11:41.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"6299263743e5ad00bda22a2539d889035e08e6e4","tid":956842,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">隔空射精落個雞煲度</span>"},{"pid":"769d243e83e4d64713200a33d5569921a66b78df","tid":956842,"uid":224666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"食得雞煲就預左㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登仔口吻"},{"pid":"2b03350e103f19e0e02bafecba714276d24c99fb","tid":956842,"uid":27482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:15:09.000Z","msg":"咁你仲去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e801d84316106dbbed4adcaf6ad2b1725c52ff79","tid":956842,"uid":3063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"用腳開唔得？"},{"pid":"1d51146e92c261c656f46df653102d5716132eb3","tid":956842,"uid":100099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"用腳喺下邊了開隻門咪得"},{"pid":"62c4e16467934e593ac9aaf4b2eb704779ad8084","tid":956842,"uid":136785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:19:43.000Z","msg":"用腳&quot;了&quot;門底咪得"},{"pid":"4fdd6dd93e0ec042e6459b09650e5b7f04060af0","tid":956842,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:23:12.000Z","msg":"用嘴吸住塊板咪得囉"},{"pid":"3f6a89c11a34a7958d120960ab683548e7f0c6be","tid":956842,"uid":8762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"識食一定入廚房屙係d 雞煲到<br />\n得你咁弱智去幾次都唔識do<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28acb2270d5988be5b